1
00:00:13,010 --> 00:00:15,810
[Episode 10]

2
00:00:31,010 --> 00:00:31,849
Take it.

3
00:00:33,730 --> 00:00:34,449
What do you mean?

4
00:00:34,730 --> 00:00:35,889
It's not like I'm asking you to do something bad.

5
00:00:36,290 --> 00:00:37,289
Why are you so nervous?

6
00:00:38,730 --> 00:00:39,889
I heard you bankrupted yourself

7
00:00:39,890 --> 00:00:40,889
to treat your father's illness.

8
00:00:41,330 --> 00:00:42,129
So

9
00:00:44,170 --> 00:00:45,649
I think you need this now.

10
00:00:48,010 --> 00:00:48,609
I don't need it.

11
00:00:48,970 --> 00:00:49,609
You can go.

12
00:00:55,610 --> 00:00:56,729
These days,

13
00:00:56,850 --> 00:00:58,689
upright officers like you

14
00:00:58,690 --> 00:00:59,689
are hard to come by.

15
00:01:02,570 --> 00:01:03,329
I'm not

16
00:01:03,570 --> 00:01:05,129
some righteous gentleman either.

17
00:01:05,330 --> 00:01:06,129
I just don't want

18
00:01:06,410 --> 00:01:07,409
to lose the job

19
00:01:07,490 --> 00:01:08,449
over small gains.

20
00:01:08,850 --> 00:01:09,569
Do you understand me?

21
00:01:10,170 --> 00:01:10,729
Understood.

22
00:01:12,450 --> 00:01:13,009
By the way,

23
00:01:13,970 --> 00:01:14,689
one more thing.

24
00:01:15,850 --> 00:01:16,809
Captain Yu,

25
00:01:17,010 --> 00:01:17,809
have you heard of a

26
00:01:17,810 --> 00:01:19,369
girl named Ye Xiaoman?

27
00:01:23,290 --> 00:01:24,729
We live under the same roof,

28
00:01:24,730 --> 00:01:25,569
coming and going together,

29
00:01:25,570 --> 00:01:26,929
spending every day together.

30
00:01:27,290 --> 00:01:28,609
Now we tell each other everything,

31
00:01:28,610 --> 00:01:29,529
share every secret.

32
00:01:35,170 --> 00:01:35,849
What?

33
00:01:36,570 --> 00:01:37,609
Is she important to you?

34
00:01:48,650 --> 00:01:49,769
Let me put it this way

35
00:01:50,330 --> 00:01:51,129
Xiaoman and I

36
00:01:51,370 --> 00:01:53,489
grew up together as childhood sweethearts.

37
00:01:53,890 --> 00:01:55,249
If it weren't for her sister's situation,

38
00:01:55,810 --> 00:01:56,969
you wouldn't be in the picture.

39
00:02:00,170 --> 00:02:00,929
Help me,

40
00:02:01,290 --> 00:02:02,289
and you help her.

41
00:02:02,690 --> 00:02:03,329
What do you mean?

42
00:02:03,370 --> 00:02:04,489
Think it through

43
00:02:04,570 --> 00:02:05,769
is the Chief more important,

44
00:02:06,250 --> 00:02:07,569
or is Ye Xiaoman?

45
00:02:19,650 --> 00:02:20,649
What are you thinking about?

46
00:02:21,330 --> 00:02:22,569
Why didn't you use the front door again?

47
00:02:23,850 --> 00:02:25,769
The front door is for upright gentlemen,

48
00:02:26,210 --> 00:02:27,089
which I'm not.

49
00:02:28,450 --> 00:02:29,209
Then please leave.

50
00:02:30,890 --> 00:02:31,849
Just kidding.

51
00:02:33,210 --> 00:02:34,129
Serious business

52
00:02:36,210 --> 00:02:38,089
the five workers killed at the docks night before last

53
00:02:38,170 --> 00:02:39,489
were beaten to death first,

54
00:02:39,610 --> 00:02:40,689
then thrown into the water,

55
00:02:40,810 --> 00:02:42,409
so it's clearly murder.

56
00:02:42,730 --> 00:02:44,129
Then Zhou Yichen's gonna slip up

57
00:02:44,130 --> 00:02:45,169
pretty soon, right?

58
00:02:46,530 --> 00:02:47,689
These few pages

59
00:02:48,010 --> 00:02:49,409
cost me a fortune,

60
00:02:49,410 --> 00:02:51,169
to get the coroner to secretly examine.

61
00:02:51,530 --> 00:02:53,009
They have no legal standing whatsoever.

62
00:02:54,210 --> 00:02:55,289
But someone

63
00:02:55,450 --> 00:02:56,569
agreed to help investigate for you.

64
00:02:57,730 --> 00:02:58,569
Someone?

65
00:03:02,290 --> 00:03:03,489
Your old flame.

66
00:03:03,690 --> 00:03:04,969
I don't have any old flames.

67
00:03:05,290 --> 00:03:06,649
Childhood sweethearts,

68
00:03:07,610 --> 00:03:08,929
innocent playmates.

69
00:03:10,210 --> 00:03:11,209
Captain Yu.

70
00:03:14,530 --> 00:03:16,169
We're not like that.

71
00:03:17,330 --> 00:03:18,249
Really?

72
00:03:24,570 --> 00:03:25,849
An He's assault must be

73
00:03:26,290 --> 00:03:27,729
connected to my sister.

74
00:03:29,010 --> 00:03:30,489
I asked your sister before,

75
00:03:30,690 --> 00:03:31,929
but she gave no explanation.

76
00:03:32,650 --> 00:03:34,769
It felt like she had some unspoken pain.

77
00:03:35,010 --> 00:03:37,009
Leaving my brother and his mom

78
00:03:37,130 --> 00:03:38,769
seemed like a relief for her.

79
00:03:39,610 --> 00:03:40,529
Relief?

80
00:03:41,090 --> 00:03:41,889
But my Second Concubine

81
00:03:41,890 --> 00:03:43,289
wasn't a good concubine either.

82
00:03:43,610 --> 00:03:44,969
She abused your sister for years.

83
00:03:45,250 --> 00:03:46,089
Luckily, on the surface,

84
00:03:46,090 --> 00:03:47,569
I had a good relationship with Second Concubine.

85
00:03:47,810 --> 00:03:49,289
I often took Chuxue to the opera.

86
00:03:50,250 --> 00:03:52,249
Gradually, she began to smile again.

87
00:03:54,090 --> 00:03:56,209
The Eldest Young Master used to treat her very well.

88
00:03:56,450 --> 00:03:58,569
He took Chuxue to support her performances every day.

89
00:03:58,850 --> 00:04:01,129
So he used opera outings as an excuse

90
00:04:01,330 --> 00:04:02,969
to help your sister.

91
00:04:03,330 --> 00:04:04,729
She suffered far fewer abuses because of it.

92
00:04:11,970 --> 00:04:12,729
Zhou Yimo,

93
00:04:14,450 --> 00:04:15,449
thank you.

94
00:04:17,410 --> 00:04:19,089
It was nothing.

95
00:04:20,090 --> 00:04:21,089
While I was gone,

96
00:04:22,650 --> 00:04:24,169
someone in this mansion

97
00:04:25,210 --> 00:04:27,089
gave her genuine warmth and kindness.

98
00:04:31,090 --> 00:04:32,409
You're being so polite

99
00:04:32,930 --> 00:04:34,489
all of a sudden.

100
00:04:36,370 --> 00:04:37,969
You had such a promising future.

101
00:04:38,530 --> 00:04:40,449
Why investigate this way?

102
00:04:40,730 --> 00:04:41,609
In this mansion,

103
00:04:41,610 --> 00:04:43,129
no one is easy to deal with.

104
00:04:43,410 --> 00:04:44,569
Everything you've done

105
00:04:44,890 --> 00:04:46,769
is ruining your own life.

106
00:04:47,250 --> 00:04:48,369
With parents gone early,

107
00:04:49,370 --> 00:04:50,329
the elder sister becomes the mother.

108
00:04:50,970 --> 00:04:52,609
She's my entire motivation.

109
00:04:52,970 --> 00:04:54,529
I know this is my obsession,

110
00:04:55,170 --> 00:04:56,169
unrelated to others.

111
00:04:56,450 --> 00:04:58,209
I've survived this long

112
00:05:00,010 --> 00:05:01,289
for my own obsessions too.

113
00:05:02,570 --> 00:05:04,409
To avenge your mother?

114
00:05:04,570 --> 00:05:05,529
Far more than that.

115
00:05:07,210 --> 00:05:07,889
What else?

116
00:05:08,810 --> 00:05:11,209
I want to reclaim all my He family's assets.

117
00:05:11,810 --> 00:05:13,449
Everything my father has now

118
00:05:13,930 --> 00:05:15,169
came from marrying my mother

119
00:05:15,170 --> 00:05:16,809
and becoming my stepfather.

120
00:05:18,210 --> 00:05:19,169
All these years,

121
00:05:19,690 --> 00:05:20,809
he's used every trick

122
00:05:20,810 --> 00:05:22,449
to swallow up the He family's wealth.

123
00:05:22,770 --> 00:05:23,929
So many maternal relatives

124
00:05:23,930 --> 00:05:25,289
lost everything because of him,

125
00:05:25,410 --> 00:05:26,569
left destitute and displaced.

126
00:05:36,210 --> 00:05:47,929
[Tomb of Ye Chuxue]

127
00:06:08,970 --> 00:06:09,969
Sister Chuxue?

128
00:06:11,890 --> 00:06:12,849
Sister Chuxue?

129
00:06:13,770 --> 00:06:14,569
Is that you?

130
00:06:15,730 --> 00:06:16,449
Sister Chuxue?

131
00:06:18,530 --> 00:06:19,289
Sister Chuxue?

132
00:06:20,570 --> 00:06:21,209
I'm sorry.

133
00:06:22,770 --> 00:06:23,489
I'm sorry.

134
00:06:26,730 --> 00:06:27,569
Second Young Master,

135
00:06:29,410 --> 00:06:30,489
I'm Fifth Concubine.

136
00:06:31,610 --> 00:06:32,609
Did you perhaps

137
00:06:33,890 --> 00:06:35,849
mistake me for someone else?

138
00:06:36,770 --> 00:06:37,529
I...

139
00:06:39,850 --> 00:06:44,289
Who is Sister Chuxue?

140
00:06:48,010 --> 00:06:49,609
Sister Chuxue...

141
00:07:03,810 --> 00:07:05,289
In this world, she was once the one

142
00:07:07,250 --> 00:07:08,409
who cherished me above all others.

143
00:07:09,970 --> 00:07:10,969
Could it be...

144
00:07:12,010 --> 00:07:13,409
this one on the tombstone?

145
00:07:14,370 --> 00:07:15,289
Ye Chuxue?

146
00:07:18,010 --> 00:07:19,489
Didn't you push me away?

147
00:07:20,690 --> 00:07:21,409
Why?

148
00:07:23,890 --> 00:07:25,289
Why the sudden concern?

149
00:07:32,490 --> 00:07:33,609
You didn't know?

150
00:07:34,570 --> 00:07:35,449
Your father

151
00:07:35,890 --> 00:07:38,169
watches my every move.

152
00:07:41,730 --> 00:07:43,409
I had no choice.

153
00:07:44,730 --> 00:07:45,849
Are you saying...

154
00:07:46,730 --> 00:07:47,769
deep down,

155
00:07:49,610 --> 00:07:50,969
you didn't want to reject me?

156
00:07:52,410 --> 00:07:52,849
Is that so?

157
00:07:54,010 --> 00:07:54,809
Of course.

158
00:08:07,410 --> 00:08:08,129
Fifth concubine,

159
00:08:09,010 --> 00:08:09,849
have some tea

160
00:08:28,010 --> 00:08:30,689
That maid Chuxue...

161
00:08:30,970 --> 00:08:32,769
was she someone you cared for?

162
00:08:33,250 --> 00:08:35,169
She used to be my personal maid.

163
00:08:36,530 --> 00:08:37,889
We were as close as siblings.

164
00:08:38,730 --> 00:08:39,609
But for some reason,

165
00:08:39,610 --> 00:08:40,849
Father suddenly transferred her

166
00:08:40,850 --> 00:08:41,889
to the Second concubine.

167
00:08:41,970 --> 00:08:43,289
Three years ago, she took her own life.

168
00:08:44,850 --> 00:08:45,809
I never expected that.

169
00:08:46,530 --> 00:08:47,609
She was doing well.

170
00:08:48,730 --> 00:08:49,649
Why transfer her?

171
00:08:50,530 --> 00:08:51,529
I don't know either.

172
00:08:52,890 --> 00:08:54,369
Father has always been unyielding.

173
00:08:54,850 --> 00:08:55,809
Second Young Master,

174
00:08:57,090 --> 00:08:58,289
have you heard of

175
00:08:58,890 --> 00:09:00,529
a woman named An He?

176
00:09:03,130 --> 00:09:03,929
An opera singer.

177
00:09:04,770 --> 00:09:05,449
I'm not familiar with her.

178
00:09:06,170 --> 00:09:06,769
Not familiar?

179
00:09:07,970 --> 00:09:08,809
Why are you suddenly

180
00:09:08,810 --> 00:09:09,969
asking about this today?

181
00:09:10,650 --> 00:09:11,849
That day at the docks,

182
00:09:13,570 --> 00:09:15,529
I heard that on New Year's Eve three years ago,

183
00:09:15,970 --> 00:09:17,689
they publicly humiliated An He.

184
00:09:18,890 --> 00:09:21,089
As the person in charge of the docks,

185
00:09:22,370 --> 00:09:23,529
you must have known about this.

186
00:09:24,570 --> 00:09:25,209
Fifth concubine

187
00:09:26,290 --> 00:09:27,089
have some tea.

188
00:09:28,970 --> 00:09:30,569
How could you not know?

189
00:09:34,570 --> 00:09:35,969
She got too close to Chuxue.

190
00:09:37,210 --> 00:09:37,889
Perhaps those workers

191
00:09:37,890 --> 00:09:39,209
just wanted to remind her

192
00:09:41,730 --> 00:09:43,529
that after all, she's just a woman.

193
00:09:51,290 --> 00:09:52,849
You're so clever and cautious.

194
00:09:53,690 --> 00:09:54,849
The poison isn't in the tea.

195
00:09:55,610 --> 00:09:56,969
It's on your cup's rim.

196
00:11:09,410 --> 00:11:10,209
You're awake

197
00:11:11,210 --> 00:11:11,849
Hungry?

198
00:11:13,850 --> 00:11:14,489
Not hungry.

199
00:11:17,130 --> 00:11:18,129
Don't worry,

200
00:11:18,410 --> 00:11:19,609
I won't drug you anymore.

201
00:11:19,930 --> 00:11:21,209
You're already here.

202
00:11:22,290 --> 00:11:23,529
What is this place?

203
00:11:25,770 --> 00:11:26,849
What do you

204
00:11:28,130 --> 00:11:29,289
intend to do?

205
00:11:30,210 --> 00:11:31,209
Starting today,

206
00:11:32,410 --> 00:11:33,249
you are free.

207
00:11:34,890 --> 00:11:36,009
What do you mean?

208
00:11:36,530 --> 00:11:37,929
You can do whatever you want.

209
00:11:39,210 --> 00:11:40,209
You can tell me

210
00:11:40,650 --> 00:11:41,689
whatever you desire.

211
00:11:42,850 --> 00:11:43,729
I will bring you

212
00:11:43,730 --> 00:11:44,649
all the finest things

213
00:11:44,810 --> 00:11:46,129
this world has to offer.

214
00:11:48,130 --> 00:11:50,129
I am the fifth concubine!

215
00:11:52,010 --> 00:11:53,249
I've been gone all night.

216
00:11:54,250 --> 00:11:55,889
Even just for appearances,

217
00:11:56,570 --> 00:11:57,689
they will come looking for me.

218
00:11:58,650 --> 00:11:59,729
Don't worry about that.

219
00:12:00,170 --> 00:12:01,329
This private residence is secluded.

220
00:12:01,570 --> 00:12:02,249
Except for you and me,

221
00:12:02,330 --> 00:12:03,129
no one else

222
00:12:03,130 --> 00:12:04,129
can find you.

223
00:12:05,010 --> 00:12:06,009
And I have arranged

224
00:12:06,650 --> 00:12:07,849
everything in the manor.

225
00:12:08,370 --> 00:12:08,929
Tomorrow night,

226
00:12:09,650 --> 00:12:10,769
all they will find is

227
00:12:11,010 --> 00:12:12,329
the bloated and rotting corpse

228
00:12:12,330 --> 00:12:14,969
of the Zhou family's Fifth Concubine.

229
00:12:16,210 --> 00:12:16,769
At that time,

230
00:12:17,210 --> 00:12:17,929
your name

231
00:12:18,170 --> 00:12:19,529
will be erased from

232
00:12:20,490 --> 00:12:21,649
the Zhou family registry.

233
00:12:25,970 --> 00:12:26,889
You're insane!

234
00:12:27,450 --> 00:12:28,449
I'm not insane.

235
00:12:29,930 --> 00:12:31,889
I know exactly what I want.

236
00:12:36,370 --> 00:12:36,889
Look,

237
00:12:37,090 --> 00:12:38,569
here are the finest clothes,

238
00:12:38,730 --> 00:12:39,729
the best jewelry,

239
00:12:40,610 --> 00:12:41,969
more than Father ever gave you.

240
00:12:42,570 --> 00:12:43,529
And this mansion

241
00:12:44,490 --> 00:12:45,569
is yours now.

242
00:12:51,370 --> 00:12:52,409
You ordered men to defile An He,

243
00:12:54,170 --> 00:12:55,369
silenced the dockworkers,

244
00:12:56,970 --> 00:12:57,809
and now

245
00:12:59,330 --> 00:13:00,689
you imprison me here.

246
00:13:01,570 --> 00:13:02,289
Zhou Yichen,

247
00:13:04,370 --> 00:13:05,689
where is your conscience?

248
00:13:09,730 --> 00:13:10,889
Conscience?

249
00:13:13,650 --> 00:13:14,409
It seems

250
00:13:15,570 --> 00:13:16,929
when I was very young,

251
00:13:18,730 --> 00:13:20,569
it was trampled underfoot

252
00:13:21,490 --> 00:13:22,489
by my own parents,

253
00:13:24,010 --> 00:13:25,729
whom I

254
00:13:28,570 --> 00:13:29,809
cared about most!

255
00:13:33,890 --> 00:13:35,329
But that no longer matters.

256
00:13:36,490 --> 00:13:37,649
Now I only know

257
00:13:39,210 --> 00:13:40,729
you're the one I want to protect most.

258
00:13:42,290 --> 00:13:43,529
I can't lose you again.

259
00:13:49,890 --> 00:13:51,089
My feet hurt.

260
00:13:51,930 --> 00:13:52,769
Please,

261
00:13:53,570 --> 00:13:54,649
remove these shackles.

262
00:13:54,770 --> 00:13:55,569
Fifth concubine

263
00:13:57,330 --> 00:13:58,249
don't play

264
00:13:58,250 --> 00:13:59,449
little games with me.

265
00:14:00,570 --> 00:14:01,209
You

266
00:14:02,850 --> 00:14:03,929
can't escape.

267
00:14:05,970 --> 00:14:07,129
I'm not trying to escape.

268
00:14:10,090 --> 00:14:11,289
I have an old foot injury.

269
00:14:11,650 --> 00:14:12,609
The shackles hurt terribly.

270
00:14:12,610 --> 00:14:13,809
If this continues,

271
00:14:15,570 --> 00:14:16,809
it'll flare up again.

272
00:14:20,610 --> 00:14:21,929
I can remove the shackles,

273
00:14:22,330 --> 00:14:23,289
but do you think

274
00:14:24,370 --> 00:14:25,889
someone will come to save you?

275
00:14:27,890 --> 00:14:29,009
On our way here,

276
00:14:29,730 --> 00:14:31,169
you kept dropping these

277
00:14:31,610 --> 00:14:32,569
bat grass leaves.

278
00:14:33,610 --> 00:14:34,769
Who were you signaling?

279
00:14:37,250 --> 00:14:38,089
My brother?

280
00:14:38,490 --> 00:14:39,489
Too bad.

281
00:14:39,770 --> 00:14:41,249
He'll never discover

282
00:14:41,250 --> 00:14:42,289
this place exists.

283
00:14:47,410 --> 00:14:49,569
[Zhou's residence]

284
00:14:49,610 --> 00:14:50,289
Master,

285
00:14:50,810 --> 00:14:52,289
we've searched every inch of Wu County,

286
00:14:52,570 --> 00:14:54,409
but still no trace of the Fifth Concubine.

287
00:14:54,570 --> 00:14:55,729
Have the police been dispatched?

288
00:14:55,970 --> 00:14:56,449
Yes,

289
00:14:56,810 --> 00:14:57,609
they're all searching.

290
00:14:58,250 --> 00:14:59,289
Wu County isn't that big.

291
00:14:59,490 --> 00:15:00,569
She went out alone last night.

292
00:15:00,570 --> 00:15:01,449
Where could she possibly go?

293
00:15:01,730 --> 00:15:03,169
Could something have happened to her?

294
00:15:05,570 --> 00:15:06,409
Master,

295
00:15:07,730 --> 00:15:08,289
Master!

296
00:15:08,730 --> 00:15:09,649
Near the docks,

297
00:15:09,650 --> 00:15:11,449
someone spotted someone resembling the Fifth Concubine

298
00:15:11,570 --> 00:15:12,489
walking along the riverbank.

299
00:15:12,490 --> 00:15:13,529
She vanished in an instant.

300
00:15:13,570 --> 00:15:15,009
Could she have fallen into the river?

301
00:15:15,210 --> 00:15:15,689
What?

302
00:15:15,690 --> 00:15:16,369
Fell into the river?

303
00:15:17,170 --> 00:15:17,769
Where's the body?

304
00:15:18,250 --> 00:15:18,929
Find her!

305
00:15:19,570 --> 00:15:20,209
I want her found,

306
00:15:20,210 --> 00:15:21,289
dead or alive!

307
00:15:21,570 --> 00:15:22,409
Father, calm down.

308
00:15:22,970 --> 00:15:23,889
I know the docks well.

309
00:15:24,290 --> 00:15:25,689
I'll find some strong swimmers to search.

310
00:15:25,890 --> 00:15:27,209
Go, go now!

311
00:15:32,370 --> 00:15:32,969
Where is Yimo?

312
00:15:33,690 --> 00:15:34,569
Why haven't we seen him

313
00:15:34,890 --> 00:15:35,889
since early morning?

314
00:15:36,650 --> 00:15:38,289
He left before dawn.

315
00:15:38,970 --> 00:15:39,969
Nanxi said

316
00:15:40,850 --> 00:15:42,529
he went to the opera house.

317
00:15:43,130 --> 00:15:44,249
Watching opera?

318
00:15:44,890 --> 00:15:46,489
While someone in the family is missing,

319
00:15:46,570 --> 00:15:47,569
he's out fooling around?

320
00:15:48,290 --> 00:15:49,689
Just wait till he gets back. I'll deal with him.

321
00:15:51,490 --> 00:15:53,449
Master, don't be angry.

322
00:15:53,890 --> 00:15:55,449
You still have Chen and me.
